    {
      "name": "3. Research Follow-up",
      "description": "Tool-based follow-up questions using Claude Haiku with direct model invocation.\n\nAvailable tools:\n- getReportSection: Fetch report sections\n- getReportRatings: Get investment ratings\n- getMetricsHistory: Historical financial data\n- getAvailableReports: List covered companies",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Ask Follow-up Question (SSE Stream)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Generate a unique session ID if not set",
                  "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('session_id')) {",
                  "    var sessionId = 'research-' + pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('session_id', sessionId);",
                  "    console.log('Generated session_id:', sessionId);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Note: This endpoint returns SSE stream",
                  "// Postman may not display the stream correctly",
                  "// Use 'Send and Download' or check raw response",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Content-Type is text/event-stream', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get('Content-Type')).to.include('text/event-stream');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "text/event-stream"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"question\": \"What does the debt analysis show for this company?\",\n    \"session_id\": \"{{session_id}}\",\n    \"ticker\": \"{{ticker}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/research/followup",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["research", "followup"]
            },
            "description": "Ask a follow-up question about investment research. Returns SSE stream.\n\nUses Claude Haiku with tool orchestration (up to 10 turns).\n\n**Required fields:**\n- `question`: Your research question\n- `session_id`: Session identifier for conversation context\n- `ticker`: Stock ticker symbol (e.g., AAPL)\n\n**Available tools the model can use:**\n- `getReportSection(ticker, section_id)` - Fetch specific report sections\n- `getReportRatings(ticker)` - Get investment ratings and verdict\n- `getMetricsHistory(ticker, metric_type, quarters)` - Historical trend data\n- `getAvailableReports()` - List all covered companies\n\n**Note:** This endpoint returns Server-Sent Events (SSE). Postman may show raw event data."
          },
          "response": []
        },
